{"title":"在假日里","authors":["韩笑"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":4,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在假日里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在假日里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军走进兵营。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士们都游戏去啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有桃花盛开的窗前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐着一个新兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他对着带花的信纸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢笔停了又停……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照片收到了没有？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天我们打靶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"首长又给我……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军站在背后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眯着慈祥的眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忍不住催他："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快写吗！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我戴上红花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若是不会写，画一个也行！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新兵以为是同乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连头也没回就说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咳！一肚子话呀就是讲不清！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军听了大笑起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吓得新兵满面绯红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他立起大声报告："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军同志！我正……正练习作文！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军拍着他肩膀说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好！祝你得个五分！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的文章很有感情！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}